title: Question:
author: roksana.hee
content: It is certainly possible that You.com could become a major player in the search engine market and eventually overtake Google. Is it possible?I know Google is the best master but my friend debet with me about You.com.What is your concept of You.com?

comments.author: mich
comments.body: Well I will admit I think google is the best search engine but I tried yours. I think it is a nice concept that gave me some similar results for google searches. I looked where I could buy some shoes I like.The thing I did enjoy abouty your seach engine is the store icons. Ths makes it quicker to find what stores have a product I searched for. Google does not have this but your search engine did take longer to return my search results.
